<section class="section_container" id="welcome">
  <div class="splash_text">
    <h3>
      We hope you will join us in the forest!
    </h3>    
  </div>
</section>
<section class="section_container" id="intro">
  <div class="flex_center">
    <img src="<%= image_url("welcome_sign.png") %>" id="welcome_sign">
  </div>
  <div class="section group">
    <div class="col span_1_of_2">
      <p>
        We are excited to spend the weekend at Wellspring Spa with our families and friends celebrating love, good food, the outdoors and a little spark of fire.
      </p>
      <p>
        We will begin the weekend with a welcome dinner <time datetime="2017-07-07 18:00">Friday night</time> to which all are invited. <time datetime="2017-07-08 07:00">Saturday morning</time> will be a wonderful time to start the day enjoying yoga in the Tom Tom Yurt.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col span_1_of_2">
      <p>
        You can then enjoy all that Mt. Rainier has to offer taking in the beauty of the outdoors that we love so. Or book a massage at the Spa. We’ll start the festivities at <time datetime="2017-07-08 16:30">4:30pm</time> with a pre-ceremony snack and drink. After the ceremony in the forest Sanctuary we’ll have a <time datetime="2017-07-08 17:30">cocktail hour</time>, then <time datetime="2017-07-08 18:30">family style dinner</time>. Cake, drinks and of course s’mores will be shared to continue the fun.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
