  <header>
    <h2 class="section_header">Things to Do Nearby</h2>
  </header>
    <div class="section group">
      <div class="col span_1_of_2">
        <p>
          Wellspring Spa has a variety of things to do on site. There are a couple <%= link_to("saunas and hot tubs", "http://wellspringspa.com/spa/") %> available to soak or bake in, and a labyrinth to wander and meditate in. Ryan’s friend Emily will be teaching yoga in the Tom Tom Yurt on Saturday morning at <time datetime="2017-07-08 07:00">7am</time> and <time datetime="2017-07-08 10:00">10am</time>. If you would like to book yourself a massage, <span class="emphasis">please email Wellspring</span> at <a href="mailto:info@wellspringspa.com">info@wellspringspa.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col span_1_of_2">
        <p>
          <%= link_to("Mt. Rainier", "http://visitrainier.com") %> is just next door and offers many things to see and do. There are trails all over the park, from short child-friendly ones to longer multi-day treks. <%= link_to("National Park Inn", "http://mtrainierguestservices.com/accommodations/national-park-inn/") %> and <%= link_to("Paradise Lodge", "http://mtrainierguestservices.com/accommodations/paradise-inn/") %> are two beautiful lodges on the south side of the park.  
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>

